          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2221-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>– this is your <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Drain the<strong> pickling liquid</strong> from the quick-pickled cucumber ribbons (set these aside for later!) into the salad</p><p>Add a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> to your salad and give this a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2221-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
