          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2221-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble your burger by filling each <strong>toasted brioche bun</strong> with a<strong> golden halloumi steak</strong>, a dollop of <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish </strong>and some<strong> quick-pickled cucumber ribbons</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
